      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7255785/" class="title-link">随笔记宋</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7255785"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/59458047/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u59458047-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59458047/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">晓走</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-18"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-18 01:20:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7255785_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  讲谈社的这套丛书，看到此处已是第七本，对于一个没有太多基础的历史爱好者而言，这是到目前为止除了三国那册之外读得最舒畅的一本。作者从唐末讲起，经北宋、南宋，到灭亡，穿插其实当时同时存在的辽、金、西夏包括蒙古等国情况，但主要是这些国家与宋打交道的情况——我猜这...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7255785_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7255785_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



